lines: It is not the mountain we conquer but ourselves.
author: <Author:0x00007f55bacc0e68>

lines: Every small positive change we make in ourselves repays us in confidence in the future.
author: <Author:0x00007f55bad18988>

lines: First, I prepare. Then I have faith.
author: <Author:0x00007f55bad00f68>

lines: We cannot always build the future for our youth, but we can build our youth for the future.
author: <Author:0x00007f55bad50608>

lines: Don't judge each day by the harvest you reap, but by the seeds that you plant.
author: <Author:0x00007f55bad39ef8>

lines: It’s better to look ahead and prepare, than to look back and regret.
author: <Author:0x00007f55bad83698>

lines: Be prepared, work hard, and hope for a little luck. Recognize that the harder you work and the better prepared you are, the more luck you might have.
author: <Author:0x00007f55bad6ba48>

lines: Never, never, never give up.
author: <Author:0x00007f55bad593c0>

lines: If you have made mistakes, even serious ones, there is always another chance for you.  What we call failure is not the falling down, but the staying down.
author: <Author:0x00007f55bada93c0>

lines: Obstacles don’t have to stop you. If you run into a wall, don’t turn around and give up. Figure out how to climb it, go through it or work around it.
author: <Author:0x00007f55bad90ca8>

lines: There is no chance, no destiny, no fate, that can hinder or control the firm resolve of a determined soul.
author: <Author:0x00007f55bade1720>

lines: A dream doesn't become reality through magic; it takes sweat, determination and hard work.
author: <Author:0x00007f55badca340>

lines: Have patience with all things, but, first of all with yourself.
author: <Author:0x00007f55bae1b358>

lines: Patience is not simply the ability to wait—it's how we behave while we're waiting.
author: <Author:0x00007f55bae03c08>

lines: Patience is a form of wisdom. It demonstrates that we understand and accept the fact that sometimes things must unfold in their own time.
author: <Author:0x00007f55bae5b2f0>

lines: Patience and tenacity of purpose are worth more than twice their weight of cleverness.
author: <Author:0x00007f55bae42778>

lines: Patience is more than simply learning to wait. It is having learned what is worth your time.
author: <Author:0x00007f55bae2bbb8>

lines: Anything is possible when you have the right people there to support you.
author: <Author:0x00007f55bae80b18>

lines: Many people will walk in and out of your life but only true friends will leave footprints in your heart.
author: <Author:0x00007f55bae69850>

lines: I would rather walk with a friend in the dark, than alone in the light.
author: <Author:0x00007f55baeb25a0>

lines: Try to be a rainbow in someone's cloud.
author: <Author:0x00007f55bae9b670>

lines: Good friends are like stars. You don't always see them, but you know they're always there.
author: <Author:0x00007f55baef4ab8>

lines: The whole purpose of education is to turn mirrors into windows.
author: <Author:0x00007f55baedde30>

lines: Intelligence plus character-that is the goal of true education.
author: <Author:0x00007f55baf27008>

lines: Children must be taught how to think, not what to think.
author: <Author:0x00007f55baf14340>

lines: One child, one teacher, one book, one pen can change the world.
author: <Author:0x00007f55baefd398>

lines: Education is for improving the lives of others and for leaving your community and world better than you found it.
author: <Author:0x00007f55baf557a0>

lines: A life lived with integrity… is a shining star in whose light others may follow in the years to come.
author: <Author:0x00007f55baf3c458>

lines: When you say 'yes' to others, make sure you aren't saying 'no' to yourself.
author: <Author:0x00007f55baf8f400>

lines: Real integrity is doing the right thing, knowing that nobody’s going to know whether you did it or not.
author: <Author:0x00007f55baf76108>

lines: The time is always right to do what is right.
author: <Author:0x00007f55bafd9fa0>

lines: Integrity is choosing courage over comfort; choosing what is right over what is fun, fast, or easy; and choosing to practice our values rather than simply professing them.
author: <Author:0x00007f55bafb5ad8>

lines: Once you choose hope, anything's possible.
author: <Author:0x00007f55bb019f60>
